{
  "texts": [
    "We also analyze the types of notes included in this study.",
    "Our analysis reveals that there are 411 different types of notes.",
    "Supplementary Fig. 1 displays the 20 most frequently encountered note types in this study.",
    "Notably, internal medicine notes and primary care notes emerge as the two most prevalent types.",
    "We also find that addendum notes rank third in frequency."
  ]
}